rComments: Dr. Siebert is so enthusiastic about his course, you can tell he really loves medieval philosophy. I wouldn't say that this course is birdy, but if you come to lecture and do the readings, you can definitely get the grade the grade you deserve, since he gives daily in class quizzes instead of midterms and exam. Great course, great lecturer !
teacherRatingTags: ["Skip class? You won't pass.", 'Inspirational', 'Clear grading criteria']
